%% Diagram: OCSP stapling inside the TLS handshake
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Server
    participant CA as CA OCSP Responder
    participant C as Client

    S->>CA: OCSP request (periodic, hours)
    CA->>S: Signed OCSP response (typ. 7-day validity)

    Note over S,C: Subsequent TLS handshakes
    C->>S: ClientHello + status_request
    S->>C: Certificate + CertificateStatus (stapled OCSP)
    C->>C: Validate stapled response (soft-fail in browsers)
